<p>Ole Gunnar Solskjaer has suggested Manchester United do not need any defensive reinforcements before the window closes.</p>

<p>The United boss is happy with the 'good partnership' developing between Eric Bailly and Harry Maguire.</p>

<p>Everton boss Carlo Ancelotti says he has faith in 'great goalkeeper' Jordan Pickford this season. </p>

<p>Ancelotti has ruled out dipping into the transfer market after Pickford made multiple errors in the Toffees' League Cup victory over Fleetwood.</p>

<p>Leicester forward Fousseni Diabaté has signed for Turkish Süper Lig side Trabzonspor on a permanent deal.</p>

<p>The Mali internatiional scored two goals in 19 Foxes appearances.</p>

<h1>lcfc can confirm that attacker Fousseni Diabaté has signed a permanent deal with Turkish Süper Lig side Trabzonspor, subject to international clearance.</h1>

<p>Fulham have made a late bid to sign Brentford forward Said Benrahma. </p>

<p>The Algerian is already thought to be in advanced talks with Premier League rivals Crystal Palace.</p>

<p>Lionel Messi has criticised the Barcelona board over their treatment of Luis Suarez during the Spanish club's latest transfer saga.</p>

<p>The Uruguayan agreed a £5.5million deal to join Atletico Madrid this week.</p>

<p>Tottenham are keen to sign defender Milan Skriniar but are unwilling to pay Inter's £46m asking price.</p>

<p>Spurs manager Jose Mourinho is hopeful of recruting a centre-back and striker before the window closes.</p>

<p>Zinedine Zidane's son, Enzo, is set to sign for Wydad Athletic Club in Casablanca. </p>

<p>The player's agent, Roberto Carlos, says the 25-year-old will  join the Moroccan club imminently.</p>

<p>Everton have identified Manchester United goalkeeper Sergio Romero as a transfer target. </p>

<p>The Toffees have reportedly contemplated signing a 'keeper to compete with error-prone No1 Jordan Pickford.</p>

<p>Mbwama Samatta has completed a move from Aston Villa to Fenerbahce on a four-year deal</p>

<p>The forward joined the Villans for Genk in January in a £8.5m transfer.</p>

<p>Barcelona will make one last effort to sign £90m-rated Lautaro Martinez from Inter Milan. </p>

<p>The departures of Arturo Vidal, Nelson Semedo and Luis Suarez have helped the Spanish club to raise funds.</p>

<p>Arsenal midfielder Lucas Torreira is close to joining Atletico Madrid on a season-long loan.  </p>

<p>Reports suggest the deal hasn't yet been completed because Arsenal want to include an obligation to buy Torreira in any loan deal.</p>

<p>Chelsea are planning to cut their oversized squad before the window closes, with up to 10 senior professionals likely to leave Stamford Bridge.</p>

<p>Blues have spent over £200m in the market this summer on players such as Timo Werner, Kai Havertz and Ben Chilwell.</p>

<p>Chris Smalling is desperate to return to Roma after being frozen out of Ole Gunnar Solskjaer's Manchester United squad. </p>

<p>The English defender made 37 appearances for the Serie A club while on loan last season. </p>
